{"tid":2049944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔該你哋唔撚好咁戇鳩，記住自己只係人哋嘅一張牌唔該","createTime":"2020-06-03T21:08:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T08:16:49.000Z","uid":164590,"like":33,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3758ebded22dcdd9ec555d25209f104824287cbd","tid":2049944,"uid":164590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T21:08:45.000Z","msg":"1. 依家咁多畫面出嚟嗰啲人搶掠，唔該唔好話支持佢哋定係點<br />\n<br />\n2. 佢哋舉住一支連俄羅斯都唔撚要嘅旗，而家全世界共產主義嘅代表就係支那國，唔該唔好同垃圾ANTIFA 有任何關係<br />\n<br />\n3. 依家美國已經開始咗打鳩支那國，你要記住香港只係人哋嘅一張牌，你自己都未搞掂自己人哋啲嘢關你撚事。老實講，其實大家依家都喺度搶緊pho<br />\n<br />\n4. 雖然美國國策係打鳩支那國，但係好明顯已經話咗俾你聽邊個做總統個力度會有唔同。自己諗吓應該撐邊個做總統<br />\n<br />\n5. 依家繼續咁博嗰啲搶掠畫面，再係咁搞多三四日一定會有反彈聲音<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">做人哋張牌就知訂，唔撚好做咁撚多戇鳩野</span>"},{"pid":"db0906fb4dcff2d722cf057a55f1f8dad5e8d33d","tid":2049944,"uid":164590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T21:16:23.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"f444cd6d8ff23ca129e7128326da5b319457e4a2","tid":2049944,"uid":164590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T21:17:47.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"547d661ccdf8847b6e425b3e09bf96bf00c733cb","tid":2049944,"uid":164590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T21:19:13.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"cb146e37d07e2a47b50934ba7a6ef968d04f1151","tid":2049944,"uid":164590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T21:21:13.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"d8ce0a2a233bdc0ae3249c0d72be03868c4514af","tid":2049944,"uid":164590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T21:23:07.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"93eacc429fc5fde39b36487fb5830a2dcd83c7cb","tid":2049944,"uid":164590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T21:24:35.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"619ef306be77050800b5fc9a4582b14bba6c95f5","tid":2049944,"uid":164590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T21:28:56.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"1d252ff7832ee152